Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.33,Thoughts,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Who goes there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.12,0:02:32.91,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.91,0:02:35.71,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This thing just talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,D-D-Don't be ridiculous!  You must have imagined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.76,0:02:39.84,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:48.10,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's hard enough to believe\Nthat this is actually a dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:50.52,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Is it really a dragon?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:53.69,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Yes, as hard as it is to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:56.90,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,A lizard's body with giant wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.78,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,\Nit's exactly what the legends describe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:09.50,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.84,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I-I-I-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.81,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}It breathed fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:30.23,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,How could a creature like this possibly exist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.60,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Am I dreaming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.48,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,How interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.08,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,It wasn't effective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.63,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He sure is tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.01,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.06,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.53,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's looking right at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:22.24,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.99,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.96,Thoughts,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I can sense your presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:46.96,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,So it's true.  The dragon definitely just said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.23,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Ultimate Tiger Hunt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:24.21,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Damn it!  How can it be so strong and tough?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:31.97,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.40,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.07,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,He spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:46.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Told you so!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.24,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I heard it too!  Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.17,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:13.28,Thoughts,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Pffft!  Are you companions of that Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.15,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:33.33,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It's so hot... and that dragon just spoke again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.54,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,He said "Warlord", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.25,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Does he have some grudge against the Seven Warlords?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.05,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.10,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.31,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,This time, I will cut him in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.76,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Right, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.20,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hot!  Hot!  Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.78,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'll knock him down to the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.28,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hot!  Hot!  Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:28.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Even his body is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.90,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Poooh- I must say, this is pleasantly cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:49.86,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Poooh- The flames are quite refreshing -pooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.66,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Ah... Stop that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:55.87,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,That tickles, it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:01.00,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Cease this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.42,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I command you to cease this, I do -poooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.92,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.13,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.13,0:08:13.17,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,There's a human sticking out of the dragon's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.89,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Huuuh?!  What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.31,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,So the one speaking earlier was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.02,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.53,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Eat wings, why don't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:52.83,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Zoro!  He's falling to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:11.32,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.40,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.86,Note,TL-Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Sure-Kill Green Star
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.33,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}One-Sword Style
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:46.01,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Draw-and-Resheathe Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.39,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Death Lion Song
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.92,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.42,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This dragon looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.84,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,We can barbecue it on the island's flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.00,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:41.61,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Nami-swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:46.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This time, I thought I'd make us a cold shellfish crÃªpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:49.00,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Along with some champagne!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:55.21,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Huh?  Are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.05,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:07.77,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:13.02,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,Damn it!  I've already inhaled a lot of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.77,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,They've all been knocked out by the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.65,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,Is this a natural gas unique to the New World?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:22.61,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,Or has someone boarded the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:27.49,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,I hope those four on the island...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:30.62,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,have a Baby Snail Phone with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:39.47,Thoughts,Sanji,0,0,0,,I have to... tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.45,0:12:15.79,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Two humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.96,Main,Man,0,0,0,,One iron man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:22.38,Main,Man,0,0,0,,And one pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.30,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Tie them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.30,Main,Man,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:31.89,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Pirates are ideal for our purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:37.89,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Even if they go missing, nobody will care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:56.88,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Let's take them straight to the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.80,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(640,544)}Punk Hazard Island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:04.50,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\pos(640,544)}The Burning Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.43,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Let's pull him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:11.06,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I say, who are you?!  Unhand me, now -pooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:12.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey!  I'm gonna get you out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.38,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hold still!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:16.52,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Heave, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.86,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tore him in half!  Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:28.78,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot, you think apologizing will fix this?!\NYou've killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:35.29,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Pooh- Am I free now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.93,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The legs are speaking!  What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:46.55,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Zombie!  Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.89,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:52.96,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,What could this mean?\NThere's no sign of his body being torn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.56,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So... does that mean he was just a pair of legs all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.11,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,He's pretty tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.95,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Who goes there?  What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.58,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I sense your presence,\Nbut I have neither eyes nor ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:19.04,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You sure are unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:23.34,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Poooh- Though I know not who you are,\Nyou will let me pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.38,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:28.63,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I will not die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.47,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,He's running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:35.38,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You shall not get away with this!  Foolish Warlord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.78,0:14:40.98,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!  Join my{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:42.41,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Cut it out, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:46.99,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And... that's how it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.15,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.16,0:14:53.33,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This dragon meat is delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:56.49,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What are these things called, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.83,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.10,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,a centaur, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.21,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,I'm a centaur!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.21,0:15:11.30,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This is awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.35,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,First he was stuck to the dragon, and now to Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.47,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's up with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.81,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.23,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Damn!\NI have been attached to something again -pooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.94,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Grrr... I could just... Let me go -pooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:28.61,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,That isn't very polite, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.30,0:15:30.32,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.24,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.87,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,See?  Of course he won't just become part of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.04,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nobody would be that obedient!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,His upper half must be in trouble somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.79,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Give those legs back to their owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.59,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Don't you have any imagination, Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:51.34,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This is just the way he is.  See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.27,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I see, so he's supposed to be a Legman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.76,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Yeah right!  Like hell I can just accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.51,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:58.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And about this dragon meat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:03.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You're gonna eat most of it anyway,\Nso you carry it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.22,0:16:10.90,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!  Come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, Zoro!  Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.66,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,The samurai and the guy who got killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.83,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.66,0:16:21.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Huh?  What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:28.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-A snow covered mountain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,No... a whole mountain of ice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:37.89,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The other half of the island, across the lake,\Nhas snow covered mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.43,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Yet this side is scorching hot\Nand covered with active volcanoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.43,0:16:43.56,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What's up with this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.77,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,This solves one mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.23,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.73,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:50.61,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,The voice on the Snail Phone said it was cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.93,0:16:53.14,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,Please, help me! {Copy-paste from 579}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.95,Flashbacks,Luffy,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.99,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,It's freezing... Is that you, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:02.16,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,My companions keep getting cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.16,0:17:04.71,Flashbacks,Voice,0,0,0,,The samurai's gonna kill us all! {End copy-paste from 579}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:10.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,So the killer samurai and his victims are over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:17.82,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,This island is so interesting!\NIt's snowing on that mountain, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.72,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,And it's so hot here... I wanna eat a snow cone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:22.43,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Idiot, you're actually going there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:24.06,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It'll be way too cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:26.56,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Besides, it's too far away!\NLet's head back to the ship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:29.20,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,How troubling.  It looks rather cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.36,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,If there are beasts there, we can take their fur coats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:33.86,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,We'll manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.50,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}No we won't!  Why are you guys set on going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Snow cones!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:40.91,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:03.68,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Ow... What are you{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.93,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I saw it!  I saw it!  I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.86,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A bird!  No, a person!  Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:07.69,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It was a person yet a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:08.52,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,A bird?  A person?  Which was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.65,Secondary,Usopp,0,0,0,,A bird?  A person?  Which was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:11.48,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Huh?  What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.77,Secondary,Usopp,0,0,0,,Huh?!  Was it a bird or a person?!  Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:12.77,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,There's nobody there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:29.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Sanji, what're you so worked up about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.54,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Oh, you're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.61,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Take a look around, and you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:38.78,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This is terrible, Franky!  We've been locked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey!  What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.21,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:52.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I was on deck eating that giant shellfish dessert,\Nand then... I can't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:57.89,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,This is just a guess,\Nbut it seems likely that someone used sleeping gas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.89,0:19:00.73,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,and captured us while we were unconscious!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:02.95,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,The ship was gassed, there's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:09.53,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.  If only I'd noticed it sooner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.43,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:29.55,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Are we gonna be sold off?\NAre they human traffickers?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:33.30,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But if they got everyone who was on the ship,\Nwhere is Brook?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.30,0:19:37.02,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I don't know.  We are the only ones here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:41.66,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,They're human traffickers,\Nso they wouldn't bother with a skeleton, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.95,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,You can't really be called a human either, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.33,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Neither can you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:45.88,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.03,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.00,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Did someone just... say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:55.29,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.49,0:20:00.59,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You there, do you enjoy a challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:02.25,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,In particular, a puzzle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.94,0:20:07.63,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Did this thing just speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:11.85,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.15,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,This thing?  How insolent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:19.32,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.24,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Huh?  An insect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.84,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Is it some new kind of Snail Phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:27.03,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,There are eight of them!  I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:29.45,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I am no pathetic insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.78,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You do not seem like bad folk...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.78,0:20:37.08,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,These are all bits of my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.65,0:20:40.79,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Forgive me,\Nbut could you put them back together for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.63,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Face?  Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:46.65,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This is a mouth, and this is an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:47.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:50.72,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.56,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,It's true!  It became a face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.02,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,No, there are quite a few parts left over!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:59.19,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Isn't it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:00.82,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:02.65,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Completely wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.74,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,No no no... This should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.53,0:21:08.87,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,We're making progress!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:10.79,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Wrong!  Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.51,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I wanna try!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.51,0:21:14.21,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:18.05,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Don't play around with other people's faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:19.38,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.80,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's become a proper face!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:28.01,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I feel some slight discomfort in my jaw and forehead...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.83,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,but, very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.68,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.88,Main,Straw Hats,0,0,0,,{\i1}A detached head is talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:34.64,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now{\i0} you notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:37.85,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,How can you be alive?!  Are you an evil spirit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.98,0:21:41.15,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I do not understand either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.56,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I was not reduced to a head by choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:48.99,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,That fellow used some queer technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:53.49,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I thought I would die upon being cut to pieces,\Nyet I found myself in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:58.07,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,To be cut up by the enemy and yet remain alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:01.35,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,is a disgrace to a warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.56,Main,Man,0,0,0,,One.  Two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.85,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.85,Main,Man,0,0,0,,And four.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:24.19,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Hello?  Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.06,0:22:28.86,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did.  I'm about to take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.43,0:22:32.03,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Four intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:33.66,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.87,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,How exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.87,0:22:40.38,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Be careful, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:41.63,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.89,0:22:59.81,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You were cut down by the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.81,0:23:02.35,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,and you're still alive, even as just a head?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:04.48,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,How?!  I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.24,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,He's like Buggy!  How strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:12.91,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I wish I could slice open my belly and let my body decay,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:17.36,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,but there are things I must do,\Neven if my greatest failure must be known!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:28.54,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,By the way, you... Do you know where we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:30.89,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,"You"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:35.39,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,How dare a female address me, a warrior, in such an informal manner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.39,0:23:42.69,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Women shall walk three steps behind men and address them with a modest grace! {Gil : Nami says 'Huh?' or something after this line. Maybe add this in?}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:47.51,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What was that, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:49.71,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve, for a severed head!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.71,0:23:52.32,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're talking to the ones who put your head back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.07,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,C-Cease this violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.07,0:23:56.12,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're still talking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:59.66,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Cease this, woman! {Gil : Originally 'Lass'. Makes me think of a scottish accent more than something a samurai would say. Maybe something like 'Girl' or just 'Woman' would be better. Alternatively, if we want to make him sound old-fashioned a bit more we could use 'Wench' or something... }
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.86,0:24:05.46,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,What kind of country do women like this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.96,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,So rude and self-centered...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.96,0:24:09.80,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:12.63,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,you must be deeply grieved \Nto have been robbed down to your underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.63,0:24:14.09,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I offer my sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.47,0:24:17.03,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I haven't been stripped!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.03,0:24:17.51,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.72,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,This is just fashion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.72,0:24:23.31,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,How lewd!  That is nothing but a breast-band, is it not?! {lol this piano music...suddenly this is a saloon! -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:25.76,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What, you don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.76,0:24:27.36,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I daresay I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.36,0:24:28.86,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.77,0:24:36.15,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Those lecherous eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.79,0:24:50.16,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It is a trap, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.16,0:24:53.93,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I think his skull's been cracked!  Doesn't it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:57.68,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It hurts... It hur... It hurts not!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:25:00.55,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,It is... merely itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:05.14,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I see, so women from other countries wear only breast-bands?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.14,0:25:06.01,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,In that case, I quite like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.52,0:25:10.28,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Incidentally, who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.28,0:25:13.57,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I heard that you were dragged here from your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.47,0:25:16.49,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.22,0:25:19.86,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.12,0:25:23.07,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,You people are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.00,0:25:27.12,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,That explains your savagery!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:30.67,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I loathe pirates.  They make me vomit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.54,0:25:40.56,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I thought that perhaps it was fate that brought us to this island of ice at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.56,0:25:42.84,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,and that maybe we could escape together.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.72,0:25:46.52,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,But regrettably, since you are pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:51.29,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a second.\NWhat do you mean "island of ice"? {should we add an "oy, oy" to the beginning of this? -Fadeout4} {Gil : I'd rather not. It sounds okay when spoken but is kind of retarded to write.}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.29,0:25:53.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,This is a burning island, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.99,0:25:58.30,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!  It's a scorching hot island where even the ocean is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:26:00.24,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.01,0:26:03.79,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.62,0:26:09.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,say that this is an island of ice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.13,0:26:12.08,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard the volcanic eruptions?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.34,0:26:16.37,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I have heard the sound of explosions from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.37,0:26:19.59,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,but I came to this island via a sea of ice floes.{tlc suggested "but I came to this island of ice via a sea of ice floes.", but I'd have shortened it anyway as redundant. -kae}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:24.60,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Cease talking to me, you abominable pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.10,0:26:28.74,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,So the winter sky I saw from the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.74,0:26:30.39,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,was real after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.36,0:26:35.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,The burning island Luffy and the others went to is an arctic island from the other side. {3 line madness!! Also, not sure if this line and the next should be "Main" or "Thoughts" style}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.86,0:26:40.48,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Basically, we've been taken to the arctic side!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.57,0:26:44.08,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Though if we want to know who brought us here, and why,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.08,0:26:46.20,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,we'll have to get out of this room and see for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.97,0:26:50.36,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,But Nami-san, the door is solid.  \NIt doesn't look like we'll be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.01,0:26:52.63,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.09,0:26:55.63,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,I've got a full tank of cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.96,0:27:06.47,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey!  Hey, hey, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.52,0:27:32.11,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,It's open.  Let's get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.11,0:27:34.70,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I see that weird body isn't just for show.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.70,0:27:37.46,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I wanna shoot beams too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.51,0:27:48.10,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.52,0:27:54.61,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You'd want to escape with us if we weren't pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.52,0:27:58.94,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Silence!  Be on your way, pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.94,0:28:03.16,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's no way for you to escape alone without a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.34,0:28:05.57,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.91,0:28:09.33,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Am I right, samurai of the Wano Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.38,0:28:13.37,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,He's a samurai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.86,0:28:17.13,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,This topknot is a hairstyle unique to the Wano Kingdom. {And how the hell would Sanji know this? -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.33,0:28:24.76,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the murderous samurai they mentioned on the Snail-Phone was him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.76,0:28:25.76,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.34,0:28:27.81,Main,Man,0,0,0,,I heard a blast from over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.81,0:28:28.64,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.64,0:28:30.73,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Could it be the pirates we captured?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.73,0:28:33.06,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, hurry!  They're coming for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.89,0:28:44.82,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We came here after receiving an emergency signal from someone you attacked, samurai! {3 line madness PART 2!! -Fadeout4}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.82,0:28:46.72,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sanji, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.72,0:28:48.62,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Just leave that scary samurai behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.87,0:28:54.62,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I would never bring dishonor upon myself by committing murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.90,0:29:01.30,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I came to this island to rescue my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.30,0:29:05.01,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I will kill all who get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.43,0:29:14.12,Main,Man,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.12,0:29:15.60,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Fire!  Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.53,0:29:23.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Stop right there!  I'll take you on!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.12,0:29:33.41,Main,Man,0,0,0,,How did they get out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.97,0:29:36.91,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Contact Master immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.17,0:29:40.17,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Who are they?! {Gil : Nami's face looks like a plastic mask}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.17,0:29:41.09,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun! {Gil : And now an ugly plastic mask}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.09,0:29:42.74,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,You brought him with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.74,0:29:45.17,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,He's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.17,0:29:47.43,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,You can blame me if anything happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.72,0:29:52.72,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,There's a door!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.39,0:30:01.65,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.78,0:30:04.64,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.73,0:30:07.99,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Gigantic... children?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.99,0:30:10.44,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,C-Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.44,0:30:12.62,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.00,0:30:17.96,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Who are these kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.96,0:30:21.94,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Perhaps this is some sort of nursery?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.94,0:30:25.67,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,They're absolutely huge.  Are they giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.67,0:30:28.33,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Did we drop anchor at an island of giants?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:31.60,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But there are some smaller kids too...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.60,0:30:34.97,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Then, maybe this facility\Ndoesn't discriminate between races?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.97,0:30:37.23,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,I don't see any adults, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.98,0:30:41.05,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Hey, who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.05,0:30:43.07,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,I don't know them...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.07,0:30:46.24,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Ah, could you be the frozen people?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.24,0:30:47.15,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Did you make it out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.15,0:30:48.40,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Frozen?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:49.82,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What's she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.66,0:30:55.74,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.74,0:30:56.86,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.86,0:30:58.16,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,It's a robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.16,0:30:59.67,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.67,0:31:01.43,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,I love robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.43,0:31:02.59,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,They're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.59,0:31:04.13,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What do you mean, best?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.09,0:31:06.84,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:12.13,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,{\i1}Robot!  Robot!  Robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.13,0:31:15.89,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Oh my, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.91,0:31:18.98,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,like {\i1}armored{\i0} me that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.06,0:31:22.56,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Hey, what did she mean by frozen people?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.56,0:31:25.07,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Oh, look!  It's a stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.07,0:31:25.52,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.52,0:31:27.49,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,A stuffed raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.49,0:31:28.96,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.96,0:31:30.40,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.58,0:31:32.28,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.28,0:31:32.78,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,I want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.42,0:31:37.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Franky is ridiculously popular with these kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.29,0:31:41.96,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Swirly eyebrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.96,0:31:44.04,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Shut up, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.04,0:31:45.79,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.79,0:31:47.79,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I say, all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:50.58,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,Do any of you know of a child named Momonosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.51,0:31:53.59,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,He is a young man, he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.21,0:31:56.76,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.76,0:31:58.80,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,The head spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.80,0:32:00.76,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.76,0:32:03.60,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!  Can you tell us{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.60,0:32:05.47,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.47,0:32:09.23,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Shut up, idiot!  We can't ask them anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.23,0:32:11.07,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,You're just scaring them whenever you speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.12,0:32:14.99,Main,Man,0,0,0,,The door to Biscuits Room is open!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.99,0:32:16.54,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.54,0:32:18.79,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's just get to the far side of the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:21.08,Main,Man,0,0,0,,It must be the pirates from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.08,0:32:22.54,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Don't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.16,0:32:32.68,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What kind of facility is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.68,0:32:33.68,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Please tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.68,0:32:36.17,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I seek a child named Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.26,0:32:39.85,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Just stop talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.85,0:32:42.10,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,A woman raised her hand against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.10,0:32:43.64,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,This is a shame for a warrior, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.64,0:32:44.98,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,I want to slice open my belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.98,0:32:48.15,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Go ahead!  You're getting on my nerves,\Nyou chauvinist pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.15,0:32:49.32,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Damn escapees!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.32,0:32:50.48,Main,Man,0,0,0,,You're not getting out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.81,0:32:55.11,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.11,0:32:58.66,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Calm down.  Guns and explosives are forbidden here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.66,0:33:00.62,Main,Man,0,0,0,,We can't use anything stronger than gas bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.01,0:33:06.42,Main,Man,0,0,0,,If we hit the children, we'll answer to the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.76,0:33:17.13,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Alright, children, out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.13,0:33:19.21,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.21,0:33:20.67,Main,Man,0,0,0,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.67,0:33:23.81,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Hey, Robot-san.\NYou aren't fom this island, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.81,0:33:28.14,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Of course not.  But, boy... I am a cybor{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.14,0:33:29.39,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Do you have a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.39,0:33:32.99,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Of course we do!  Our Sunny is the world's{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.99,0:33:34.19,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.53,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.53,0:33:39.48,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Please, save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.48,0:33:41.79,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What do you mean, save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.79,0:33:43.74,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,This isn't a nursery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.96,0:33:48.97,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,We're not sick any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.97,0:33:50.58,Main,Biyo,0,0,0,,We're all fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.58,0:33:53.04,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sick?  With what disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.86,0:34:04.60,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Those damn brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.60,0:34:06.69,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.69,0:34:08.81,Main,Sind,0,0,0,,Let us out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.81,0:34:11.19,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Please, Lady!  Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.65,0:34:14.48,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Now, wait up, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.99,0:34:18.95,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sorry... we're being chased, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.16,0:34:33.47,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.47,0:34:35.13,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Hey, let's take them with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.13,0:34:38.71,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Idiot!  We don't even know where to go ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.71,0:34:42.47,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,What good would come\Nfrom bringing all those kids along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.89,0:34:45.07,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.07,0:34:46.77,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,am I feeling so sad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.99,0:35:05.07,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.82,0:35:08.00,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,{\i1}come save us later!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.08,0:35:16.51,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,I know, even though\NI haven't gone outside the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.15,0:35:19.84,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,This island is empty, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.84,0:35:23.80,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,There's no town here and no people!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.80,0:35:26.31,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,That's why nobody has come to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.31,0:35:29.51,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,I wanna see Mommy and Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.39,0:35:34.55,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Lady!  Please come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.55,0:35:37.18,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Come back to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.89,0:35:41.98,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Let's help these children!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.72,0:35:45.58,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Nami-san?!  There's no reason to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.99,0:35:50.53,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,They even said they were sick!  This might be a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.21,0:35:55.16,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,We only just met them, \Nand we don't know what's going on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.16,0:35:57.38,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,It's not like we're a charity that rescues children!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.19,0:36:03.68,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Do you think I don't know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.46,0:36:08.11,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,But when children are crying for me to save them...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.11,0:36:10.63,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,how can I turn my back on them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.02,0:36:13.80,Main,Mocha,0,0,0,,Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.80,0:36:15.86,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Quickly, they're getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.86,0:36:17.44,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Those kids are in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.44,0:36:19.36,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Who cares?!  Kill them aswell!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.36,0:36:20.61,Main,Man,0,0,0,,But Master will...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.61,0:36:22.36,Main,Man,0,0,0,,It's still better than letting them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.24,0:36:30.41,Main,Nami,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun! {OMG SANJI HAS TURNED INTO A SUPER-SAIYAN!!!}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.41,0:36:31.95,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Swirly bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.84,0:36:42.17,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.17,0:36:43.94,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.94,0:36:46.04,Main,Kinemon,0,0,0,,is incredibly skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.04,0:36:46.89,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.61,0:36:58.97,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Raccoon Dog-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.95,0:37:13.49,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,{\i1}A rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:18.91,Main,Man,0,0,0,,T-They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.84,0:37:22.92,Main,Man,0,0,0,,not running away anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.76,0:37:27.51,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,When Nami-san is kind...{\alpha&HFF&} (only ever to children)...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.51,0:37:29.43,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,When Nami-san is kind... (only ever to children)...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.43,0:37:32.38,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,she is truly wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.38,0:37:34.23,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'm falling for her all over again!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.48,0:37:43.35,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Chopper.  You go on ahead with Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.35,0:37:45.17,Main,Chopper,0,0,0,,Sure, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.70,0:37:51.24,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Hey, kids!  Follow the beautiful lady and the Kung Fu raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:54.50,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'll hold back the pursuers!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.08,0:37:57.55,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,But don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.78,0:38:03.82,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,I'm only responding\Nto the longing in Nami-san's heart to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:09.34,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,If anything,\NI hate you for stealing Nami-san's affection!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.34,0:38:11.05,Main,Kid,0,0,0,,Thanks, swirly bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.05,0:38:13.06,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Shut it, you damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.09,0:38:16.27,Main,Franky,0,0,0,,Now, bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.02,0:38:28.36,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,I see.  This door can absorb any impact, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:29.11,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.70,0:38:33.16,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,...there are burn-marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.45,0:38:36.79,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Just who are those people?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.79,0:38:41.79,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,I thought {\i1}he{\i0} was the only one with the technology to make lasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.79,0:38:46.92,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,This reminds me of that despicable Vegapunk's Pacifista!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.41,0:38:51.35,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,You still haven't captured the escapees?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.35,0:38:54.18,Main,Man,0,0,0,,They should have them cornered in the Biscuit Room by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.18,0:38:56.31,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,The Biscuit Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.93,0:38:59.94,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Master, are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.64,0:39:02.27,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Yes, I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.15,0:39:08.27,Main,Man,0,0,0,,A warship from G-5 is approaching the Northwest side of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.27,0:39:11.49,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,A warship?!  Drive it off at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.41,0:39:14.53,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Release a large volume of poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.54,0:39:19.92,Main,Ceasar,0,0,0,,Just don't kill them.  If you do, the Government might figure out what we're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.92,0:39:20.79,Main,Man,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.63,0:39:25.13,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,548)\fad(500,0)}Punk Hazard Island, The Burning Lands
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.58,0:39:25.13,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What?!  Nami and the others are gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.13,0:39:27.21,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,You mean you're alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.21,0:39:30.51,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And when you woke up, there was snow and ice all around you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.37,0:39:33.35,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.35,0:39:37.39,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I was so surprised!  I felt like a bone in a thunderstorm! {The phrase he uses is literally "like my bones were hit by a pigeon-bullet". I looked it up, and it appears to be a play on the Japanese proverb é³©ãè±éç ²ãé£ã£ããã, (literally "Like a pigeon being shot by a bean-bullet") which is apparently an expression of being extremely surprised, and it says that the English equivalent of this term is "Like a duck in a thunderstorm".} {Gil: Oh god...}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.81,0:39:39.60,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.60,0:39:42.40,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No wait, like thunder in a duckstorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.40,0:39:45.28,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,No, a duck in a bonestorm? {Gil : This is horrible...}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.28,0:39:46.36,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Well, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.91,0:39:50.20,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Ah, pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.20,0:39:54.95,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Were they trying to steal the cargo on the Sunny?  Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.08,0:40:05.91,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Well, I really don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.30,0:40:10.97,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.97,0:40:12.97,Flashbacks,Brook,0,0,0,,who are you fellows?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.72,0:40:17.17,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I took them out before I got a chance to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.01,0:40:21.30,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,They all appear to be wearing some kind of gas masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:27.23,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Gas masks?  Perhaps they used some sort of sleeping gas?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.23,0:40:31.32,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,And then those people took the Sunny to the opposite side of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.60,0:40:33.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Dammit, I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.53,0:40:36.99,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You sure are fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.70,0:40:42.44,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,You did quite well yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.44,0:40:45.08,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go again!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.08,0:40:47.46,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,No matter how many times you try{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.11,0:40:49.08,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.08,0:40:50.92,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,What are you goofing around for?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.92,0:40:53.93,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Well, I just can't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.93,0:40:57.05,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Are there really intruders here?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.05,0:41:00.85,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,All I've found are a funny guy with talking hind-legs and his group.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.85,0:41:02.72,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,He is the intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.89,0:41:06.68,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Come on!  Let's keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.56,0:41:12.05,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Where are Nami-san and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.05,0:41:16.36,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Since they didn't leave behind a message, \Nit seems likely they were taken somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.36,0:41:21.45,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I get it!  Since you're a skeleton,\Nthey must have assumed you were just a corpse!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.45,0:41:25.41,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,I see, so that's why I was left behind!  Such luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.41,0:41:30.87,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,The enemy thinks they've captured all of us.\NAre there any buildings or traces of people nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.87,0:41:35.00,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Oh, Robin-san, your reasoning is so sharp.  It's like you can see everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.68,0:41:36.98,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,There is...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.97,0:41:39.26,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.98,0:41:43.27,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,A truly massive one!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.97,0:41:46.47,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.47,0:41:49.56,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,Brook, we're hurrying over there, so wait for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.56,0:41:50.62,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,Robin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.62,0:41:54.15,Main,Brook,0,0,0,,When you get here, may I see your{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.49,0:41:57.57,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,Is our enemy someone from the Government?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.57,0:42:01.16,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Who knows?  Let's hope they're at least human.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.16,0:42:03.02,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,I mean, so far we've seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.29,0:42:06.37,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,a fire-breathing dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.82,0:42:08.46,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,a half-man,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.29,0:42:11.00,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,and a bird-lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.96,0:42:17.80,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,And then there's that centaur Luffy just befr{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.92,0:42:20.72,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Now listen here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.72,0:42:22.30,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,What?!  What's gotten into you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.43,0:42:24.67,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.30,0:42:30.85,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,I let my guard down.  I thought you were on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.36,0:42:38.61,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Why can't I be?\NWe're already friends, so don't attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.32,0:42:42.49,Main,Centaur,0,0,0,,Die, intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.49,0:42:43.79,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,There's another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.63,0:42:52.79,Note,TL Note,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Bellflower
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.76,0:43:05.99,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,A leopard and a giraffe, huh? {Gil: What is this? Enies Lobby?}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.68,0:43:10.85,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Looks like there are all kinds of centaurs.  How fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.31,0:43:15.31,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,They're fictional horses!\NTheir very existence is bizarre!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.32,0:43:22.07,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Look at this Baby Snail-Phone!  It's got "CC" written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.66,0:43:25.83,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,They're not wild centaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.83,0:43:27.91,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,It must be some sort of organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.91,0:43:32.56,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,In any case, even if we do return to the fiery ocean, the Sunny won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.56,0:43:36.17,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,We've got no choice but to head for the arctic lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.17,0:43:40.54,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Nami, Sanji, Franky and Chopper have all gone missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.54,0:43:44.68,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,They've most likely been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.68,0:43:48.06,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,I just hope they haven't been shot full of holes by a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.06,0:43:50.09,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cut that out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.09,0:43:54.60,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,It'd have been faster if we just dropped anchor on the other side of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.60,0:43:59.44,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,But then we wouldn't have been able to eat that dragon meat or meet Legson!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.44,0:44:00.78,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,And who is Legson?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.78,0:44:03.65,Main,Luffy,0,0,0,,Oh, that's my back legs' name!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.65,0:44:06.94,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go!  We're changing our objective!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.94,0:44:09.91,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,Head for the frozen lands to rescue our crewmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.91,0:44:13.38,Main,Robin,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,592)}I wonder if anyone will be selling winter clothing along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.87,0:44:17.42,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,If we go there dressed like this, we'll seriously die.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.42,0:44:19.21,Main,Usopp,0,0,0,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.51,0:44:21.38,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,Vice-admiral Smoker!  We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.05,0:44:25.34,captions_soft,Caption,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,546)\fad(500,0)}The Northwestern Shore
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.38,0:44:23.55,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,I-I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.55,0:44:25.34,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Gas is still leaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.34,0:44:30.35,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,Ever since that damn Vegapunk's weapon experiments failed four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.35,0:44:32.85,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,the whole island's gone rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.19,0:44:37.37,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,More importantly, I can't see Straw Hat Luffy's pirate ship anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.37,0:44:42.86,Main,Marine,0,0,0,,There's no way anyone would come ashore with this much poisonous gas around.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.16,0:44:45.57,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.29,0:44:49.76,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,It's unnatural for there to be this much gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.76,0:44:51.70,Main,Tashigi,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.70,0:44:57.18,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Two years ago, this was just a deserted island, with no fire or ice on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.45,0:45:03.03,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,Surprisingly enough, most of the toxic materials had dissipated by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.01,0:45:07.85,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,That's why Akainu and Aokiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.85,0:45:09.80,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,chose Punk Hazard...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.80,0:45:12.55,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,as the site of their duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.19,0:45:33.41,Main,Smoker,0,0,0,,A battle fierce enough to alter the climate!
